This place is the best! So glad I found them. Typically whenever I need a new watch battery, I just go to the Fast Fix spot in the mall. After being overcharged several times and them not honoring the 5 year battery warranty I'd purchased, I decided I'd had enough.   I found PV on Yelp and decided to check it out. I was immediately greeted by friendly staff upon entering and they offer a FREE battery your first time in. They also steam cleaned and buffed my silver watch. Not to mention, they untangled some small knots in my gold chain at no additional charge while I waited. I'll definitely be coming back and would refer anyone I know that needs jewelry repair.   Justin

